Package: causalmetrics
Title: Causal Inference Toolkit for Applied Empirical Research
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Weiheng", "Zhang", email = "weiheng.zhang@utdallas.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An opinionated workflow layer for causal inference and
    reduced-form empirical analysis. Wraps fixest, grf, rdrobust, and other
    backends with unified diagnostics, data preparation utilities, and
    publication-ready output. Built on data.table for performance.
